snippet.title: Wink Feature Complete Celebration
snippet.description:
I'm excited to announce that Wink is feature complete. That means everything has been coded into the game and now my job is to fix bugs and then release it.

I'm making my way through the list of known bugs and people are submitting new ones in the Discord and I'm feverishly fixing them

If you've ever been interested in Beta/Bug testing, now is the best time! I want to make sure this game is in great shape for the cartridge release since you can't send a software update to a Gameboy Cartridge!

To join the beta testing, go to my Discord and let me know you came for bug testing. I'll add you to the Wink Beta Channel

In the meantime, here's a trailer of sorts with some footage of the exciting new features I added:
